    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you may notice some typical wear-and-tear sounds expected at this age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows visible staining and some thinning in the driver's seat. It has been regularly serviced, making it a dependable choice for a daily commute or a first car, provided you are comfortable with its well-loved appearance.",
