    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and offering an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning collector. A rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of this model.",
